{"ja452:0.1":"Jataka ","ja452:0.2":"Dasakanipata ","ja452:0.3":"Catudvaravagga ","ja452:0.4":"14. Bhuripannajataka ","ja452:1.1":"“Saccam kira tvam api bhuripanna, ","ja452:1.2":"Ya tadisi siri dhiti mati ca; ","ja452:1.3":"Na tayatebhavavasupanitam, ","ja452:1.4":"Yo yavakam bhunjasi appasupam”. ","ja452:2.1":"“Sukham dukkhena paripacayanto, ","ja452:2.2":"Kala kalam vicinam chandachanno; ","ja452:2.3":"Atthassa dvarani avapuranto, ","ja452:2.4":"Tenaham tussami yavodanena. ","ja452:3.1":"Kalanca natva abhijihanaya, ","ja452:3.2":"Mantehi attham paripacayitva; ","ja452:3.3":"Vijambhissam sihavijambhitani, ","ja452:3.4":"Tayiddhiya dakkhasi mam punapi”. ","ja452:4.1":"“Sukhipi heke na karonti papam, ","ja452:4.2":"Avannasamsaggabhaya puneke; ","ja452:4.3":"Pahu samano vipulatthacinti, ","ja452:4.4":"Kinkarana me na karosi dukkham”. ","ja452:5.1":"“Na pandita attasukhassa hetu, ","ja452:5.2":"Papani kammani samacaranti; ","ja452:5.3":"Dukkhena phuttha khalitapi santa, ","ja452:5.4":"Chanda ca dosa na jahanti dhammam”. ","ja452:6.1":"“Yena kenaci vannena, ","ja452:6.2":"muduna darunena va; ","ja452:6.3":"Uddhare dinamattanam, ","ja452:6.4":"paccha dhammam samacare”. ","ja452:7.1":"“Yassa rukkhassa chayaya, ","ja452:7.2":"nisideyya sayeyya va; ","ja452:7.3":"Na tassa sakham bhanjeyya, ","ja452:7.4":"mittadubbho hi papako. ","ja452:8.1":"Yassapi dhammam puriso vijanna, ","ja452:8.2":"Ye cassa kankham vinayanti santo; ","ja452:8.3":"Tam hissa dipanca parayananca, ","ja452:8.4":"Na tena mettim jarayetha panno”. ","ja452:9.1":"“Alaso gihi kamabhogi na sadhu, ","ja452:9.2":"Asannato pabbajito na sadhu; ","ja452:9.3":"Raja na sadhu anisammakari, ","ja452:9.4":"Yo pandito kodhano tam na sadhu. ","ja452:10.1":"Nisamma khattiyo kayira, ","ja452:10.2":"nanisamma disampati; ","ja452:10.3":"Nisammakarino raja, ","ja452:10.4":"yaso kitti ca vaddhati”ti. ","ja452:11.1":"Bhuripannajatakam cuddasamam. "}